lexer.c:
* Added: LexSet( Lexer*, TkType ) to snapshot / store current line and column
	position.
* Changed: LexChar( Lexer*, TkType ) now does what LexEat( Lexer*, TkType )
	formerly did. It calls LexSet() and LexNext().
* Changed: LexEat() is now only used for multi-char tokens. It updates token
	type and advances.
* LexNum( ) now calls LexNext( ).
* Added: .ln and .col to tokens in place of .
* Fixed: LexLine( ) not advancing the stream.